data.description: Introducing 228 Muirfield Drive, an exceptional home nestled within the prestigious Carolina Country Club, a gated golf community. Situated on a peaceful cul-de-sac lot, surrounded by lush trees, privacy and tranquility abound. The main floor of this residence features three spacious bedrooms and two full baths, providing ample space for comfortable living.  The heart of this home is the expansive kitchen, complete with a generous breakfast area. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring abundant cabinetry for all your storage needs, granite counters, and stainless steel appliances that effortlessly combine style and functionality.Whether you are hosting a gathering or enjoying a quiet evening at home, this cozy abode is sure to be your happy place. The open layout allows for easy flow and seamless entertaining, creating the perfect space for making lasting memories. The large laundry/mud room is conveniently located between the kitchen and 2-car garage. This unique home also features a second living quarters with its own 1-car garage, offering unparalleled convenience and flexibility.  Recent updates (within the last year) include 2 new water heaters, addition of the kitchenette with new flooring, 2 new toilets, new lighting on main floor, new carpet, and paint. With its prime location in the Carolina Country Club, this property offers not only a luxurious lifestyle but also access to a range of amenities, including a championship golf course, tennis courts, swimming pools, and a clubhouse with dining options. Don't miss the opportunity to own this exceptional home in a highly sought-after community.
